#MEM id=responsive-design source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/responsive-design/SKILL.md savings=2%
M||tx|---
M||name|responsive-ds
M||desc|mi's responsive ds framework for yv's glass morphism sy. Covers breakpoints, mobile glass adaptations, touch targets, fluid typography, and the responsive pass checklist for each screen.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|yv's glass morphism ds sy (V1–V4 containers, backdrop-blur, layered gradients) was built desktop-first. Mobile requires deliberate adaptation — backdrop-blur is GPU-expensive on mobile, glass overlays collapse at narrow widths, and touch targets are a separate constraint from click targets. This skill prevents mi from shipping a screen that looks correct on desktop but breaks on mobile.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|When|it|Any new screen bd
M|When|it|Any existing screen responsive pass (flagged in sn.md)
M|When|it|When a cp uses `backdrop-filter`, `glass-*` class, or layered gradient background
M|When|it|Before any screen is marked "done" in dn's sprint tracking
M|When|tx|---
M|YVON|tx|```css
M|YVON|tx|/* globals.css — use these exact custom properties */
M|YVON|--bp|480px   /* small phones */
M|YVON|--bp|768px   /* tablets and large phones landscape */
M|YVON|--bp|1024px  /* desktop default */
M|YVON|--bp|1280px  /* wide desktop */
M|YVON|tx|```
M|YVON|Tail|`sm: (640)`, `md: (768)`, `lg: (1024)`, `xl: (1280)`.
M|YVON|**Mo|** Base CSS = mobile. Augment w/ `md:` and `lg:` breakpoints. Never write desktop-first and try to override down.
M|YVON|tx|---
M|Glas|tx|\| Property \| Desktop \| Mobile (< 768px) \|
M|Glas|tx|\|----------\|---------\|-----------------\|
M|Glas|tx|\| `backdrop-blur` \| `blur(20px)` \| `blur(8px)` — GPU perf \|
M|Glas|tx|\| Glass opacity \| `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` \| `rgba(255,255,255,0.12)` — more visible on small screens \|
M|Glas|tx|\| Border radius \| `16–24px` \| `12px` — tighter on small viewport \|
M|Glas|tx|\| Padding (glass card) \| `24px` \| `16px` \|
M|Glas|tx|\| Box shadow depth \| Full 3-layer \| Single layer — mobile doesn't need depth \|
M|Glas|| `b|1px solid rgba(...)` \| Keep \| Keep — defines container edge clearly \|
M|Glas|tx|**Disable backdrop-blur completely on screens narrower than 380px.** Use a solid background fallback.
M|Glas|tx|---
M|Touc|All |
M|Touc|tx|```
M|Touc|Mini|44px × 44px (Apple HIG) / 48dp × 48dp (Material)
M|Touc|Spac|≥ 8px
M|Touc|tx|```
M|Touc|Comm|
M|Touc|it|Tab buttons in ce dashboard (often < 32px tall) → add `min-h-[44px]` on mobile
M|Touc|it|Icon buttons in NavBar → ensure `p-3` minimum
M|Touc|it|Small KPI delta badges w/ `onClick` → wrap in a larger hit area
M|Touc|tx|---
M|Typo|YVON|
M|Typo|tx|\| Element \| Desktop \| Mobile \|
M|Typo|tx|\|---------\|---------\|--------\|
M|Typo|tx|\| KPI values (52px) \| `text-[52px]` \| `text-[32px]` \|
M|Typo|tx|\| Page title (48px) \| `text-[48px]` \| `text-[28px]` \|
M|Typo|tx|\| Section labels (12px) \| `text-[12px]` \| `text-[12px]` — do not reduce further \|
M|Typo|tx|\| Body text (14px) \| `text-[14px]` \| `text-[14px]` — floor, do not reduce \|
M|Typo|Use |
M|Typo|tx|```css
M|Typo|font|clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);  /* scales from 28px to 52px */
M|Typo|tx|```
M|Typo|tx|---
M|Resp|Befo|
M|Resp|tx|```
M|Resp|tx|□ No horizontal scroll at any breakpoint
M|Resp|tx|□ Glass containers visible (not invisible at < 768px)
M|Resp|tx|□ Touch targets ≥ 44px for all interactive elements
M|Resp|tx|□ Text does not overflow glass card bounds
M|Resp|tx|□ Navigation is accessible (mobile menu or collapsed state)
M|Resp|tx|□ KPI values do not clip at 375px
M|Resp|tx|□ Scrollable lists have visible scroll indicator on touch
M|Resp|tx|□ No fixed-width elements wider than 100vw
M|Resp|tx|□ backdrop-blur disabled or reduced at < 768px
M|Resp|tx|□ All images use nx/im w/ responsive sizes prop
M|Resp|tx|```
M|Resp|tx|Fail any item → fix before marking done.
M|Resp|tx|---
M|Scre|tx|\| Screen \| Known mobile issues \| Fix \|
M|Scre|tx|\|--------\|--------------------\|----\|
M|Scre|tx|\| ce Command Dashboard \| Tab row overflows on 375px \| Horizontal scroll on tabs + `scroll-snap-x` \|
M|Scre|| An|` \|
M|Scre|tx|\| War Room \| Chat bubbles overflow glass container \| `max-w-[calc(100%-32px)]` on message cards \|
M|Scre|tx|\| cr \| Wide data tables \| `overflow-x-auto` wrapper + `min-w-[600px]` on table \|